tarve, who has housing and who remains homeless, and which families are broken up by the state. In the process, they weaken democracy and betray our most cherished national values.  This deeply researched and passionate book could not be more timely.}, publisher={Macmillan}, author={Eubanks, Virginia}, year={2018}, language={English} }
